      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ok. I think this is supposed to work like drawImage (with a color image) where RGB of paint is ignored. It\u0027d be nice if in the future we can use a paint setup at 297 that gives us the right color to provide in the text op but that may require a cascade of additional changes/simplifications of a paint setup. What you have here is definitely progress towards simplification.",
